Class CompanyRepresentative

java.lang.Object
model.User
model.CompanyRepresentative
public class CompanyRepresentative extends User
Represents a company representative who can create and manage internship opportunities. Company representatives must be approved by staff before they can post internships. Each representative can create up to MAX_INTERNSHIPS opportunities.
Since:
2025-11-16
Version:
1.0
Author:
NTU SC2002 Group
